<aside class="modal-panel connect-another-device">
  <header>
    <h1 id="fxa-why-connect-another-device-header">{{#t}}Why sync multiple devices?{{/t}}</h1>
  </header>

  <p>
    {{#t}}The Sync service isn’t a permanent backup, it’s simply a secure way to transfer saved bookmarks, history and passwords between your own devices.{{/t}}
  </p>
  <p>
    {{#t}}You should install Firefox and sync at least two devices to protect against losing your data if you need to restore it but forget your password.{{/t}}
  </p>
  <div class="button-row">
    <button id="back" type="submit">{{#t}}Got it{{/t}}</button>
  </div>
</aside>
